name: Lintang Waluku
description: Lintang Waluku is one of the most famous constellation in Indonesia well known by a lot of farmers as a sign to start planting and a sign to harvest. Internationally, Lintang Waluku is known as constellation of Orion which showing a figure of a hunter with arrow, but when we look these stars under the sky of Indonesia, this constellation will resemble to the traditional plow tools that is often used in Indonesia in the past. Three stars of Lintang Waluku are located on the crown of the man, as a visualitation of "living mind" and a reminder to always look after things around us.
